name: Crest-testing
tagline: Test bed for the EVE Online CREST API, demonstrates API access
body:
### CREST API Tester

Use for testing that CREST works and for getting a dump of endpoints. The developer console can be used to exploring these API endpoints further.

### Rate Limits

This is *not* rate limited so please use caution when executing for loops in console or something like that. Do not exceed the CREST rate limits or I'll get very very mad :)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
